Package io.github.kale_ko.bjsl.elements

Class ParsedPrimitive

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.kale_ko.bjsl.elements.ParsedElement
      • io.github.kale_ko.bjsl.elements.ParsedPrimitive
  • public class ParsedPrimitive
extends ParsedElement
    A wrapper for a primitive object used to represent String/int/float/etc. values

    Note: Values are often not stored as their normal type but rather higher bit types for ease of conversion

    Since:
    1.0.0
    Version:
    1.0.0
